annotation.text: This process will run on a daily basis at 00:00 BST. The time can be configured accordingly.

1. Fetches all the documents from the folders of the Data Export of Multi Track. 2. Checks if the created date of the documents are more than the specified threshold number of days limit, right now its 30 days. 3. Gets all the documents from the fetched documents that crosses the limit in #2 4. Deletes the documents obtained in #3.
